OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and breezy across much of
OL,6,Fthe region, although some light rain
OL,7,Fin the far southeast quickly clearing
OL,8,Fduring the early morning. Plenty of
OL,9,Fprolonged sunny spells, especially
OL,10,Fthrough the afternoon. Temperatures
OL,11,Fslightly above average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA pleasant evening with
OL,14,Fwidespread sunshine and easing winds
OL,15,Ffor many, followed by a mostly clear
OL,16,Fnight. Remaining breezy along Norfolk
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,18,
OL,19,CFriday:FVariable cloud on Friday, but
OL,20,Fplenty of sunny spells through the
OL,21,Fday. Warm to very warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
