OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fat times with variable cloud for much
OL,7,Fof the period, staying mostly dry.
OL,8,FTemperatures likely above average,
OL,9,Fperhaps becoming very warm or hot in
OL,10,Fplaces.
